  "detailed_description": "Welcome to Rumple Town!<br><br>Get ready for a turn based, card drafting adventure. Use your deck building and tactical skills to draft a deck that is strong enough to best the oncoming monsters. <br><br>Each card can be upgraded twice.<br><br>Summon Totems during combat, which will give you all sorts of benefits.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2107040/extras/04f3ba49c98ef25325e057905842c922.poster.avif?t=1700136102\" width=377 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2107040/extras/04f3ba49c98ef25325e057905842c922.webm?t=1700136102\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Learn different card synergies, which will help you defeat the toughest of monsters.<br><br>You will collect constructs in your adventure which you will keep from battle to battle.<br><br>After surviving through each year, the monsters will become stronger and new mechanics will be introduced.<br><br>At Rumple Level 15, get ready for the Rumple Town RockStars which will help you during your campaign.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2107040/extras/d403df5f8d99772d1051667f0a0b804f.poster.avif?t=1700136102\" width=400 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2107040/extras/d403df5f8d99772d1051667f0a0b804f.webm?t=1700136102\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
